      <title>中国人民银行准备通过各大银行发行数十亿元人民币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行采取了进一步措施，通过出售国债来冷却创纪录的股市上涨，并表示目前通过与贷款机构达成的协议，央行可以持有“数千亿元”人民币的国债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
